## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [CS68146]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Pale cotyledons and green true leaves in 14 day-old seedlings. Delayed seedling development.
   - [CS68147]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Pale green plants.
   - [CS68148]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Pale green plants.
   - [SALK_072931]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;few flower development defects
   - [qwrf1qwrf2]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Severely deformed morphologies and symmetries of various floral organs as well as a significant reduction in the seed setting rate.
   - [sco3-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;The sco3-1 mutation alters chloroplast morphology and development, reduces chlorophyll accumulation, impairs thylakoid formation and photosynthesis in seedlings, and results in photoinhibition under extreme CO(2) concentrations in mature leaves.
